title: Crash while logging in after switching network from Mainnet to Ropsten
body:
### Description

*Type*: Bug

*Summary*: The app crashed when I recovered an account, logged in, switched from Mainnet to Ropsten and then tried to log in again. Happened on Android. I could not reproduce it.

### Reproduction

- Open Status
- Recover an account
- Switch from Mainnet to Ropsten
- Log in 

### Additional Information
* Status version: nightly, June 12
* Operating System: Android
I mentioned this crash in a comment in https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/3981
